    "body": "Minimize to `setResizable()` API bug. Each time calling `setResizable(false)` in a frameless window, the height of the window will increase, and the increased number each time seems to be the height of title bar(about 22px).\n\nA minimal sample:\n\n```\nvar BrowserWindow = require('browser-window');\n  var win = new BrowserWindow({\n    frame: false\n });\nwin.setResizable(false);\nwin.setResizable(false);\n```\n"
